ken punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token class-name\">String</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span> strs <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"Hello\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"World\"</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<ul>\n<li>같은 타입의 여러 변수를 하나의 묶음으로 다루는 것</li>\n<li>연속적인 메모리 공간에 저장</li>\n<li>배열의 이름은 배열을 가리키는 참조변수</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"배열의-선언과-생성-초기화\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EB%B0%B0%EC%97%B4%EC%9D%98-%EC%84%A0%EC%96%B8%EA%B3%BC-%EC%83%9D%EC%84%B1-%EC%B4%88%EA%B8%B0%ED%99%94\" aria-label=\"배열의 선언과 생성 초기화 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>배열의 선언과 생성, 초기화</h2>\n<h3 id=\"1-배열의-선언\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#1-%EB%B0%B0%EC%97%B4%EC%9D%98-%EC%84%A0%EC%96%B8\" aria-label=\"1 배열의 선언 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>1. 배열의 선언</h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"java\"><pre class=\"language-java\"><code class=\"language-java\"><span class=\"token comment\">// int 배열 선언</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">int</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span> numbers<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>이렇게 <code class=\"language-text\">[]</code>을 변수 이름 뒤에 적어도 상관 없다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"java\"><pre class=\"language-java\"><code class=\"language-java\"><span class=\"token keyword\">int</span> numbers<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"2-배열의-생성\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#2-%EB%B0%B0%EC%97%B4%EC%9D%98-%EC%83%9D%EC%84%B1\" aria-label=\"2 배열의 생성 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>2. 배열의 생성</h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"java\"><pre class=\"language-java\"><code class=\"language-java\"><span class=\"token comment\">// 길이 10의 int 배열 생성</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">// 0으로 초기화됨</span>\nnumbers <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">int</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token number\">10</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>앞에서 배열을 선언한 것은 배열을 가리킬 참조변수를 선언했을뿐이고,\n실제 배열이 메모리에 생성되는 것은 이렇게 <code class=\"language-text\">new</code>에 의해서.</p>\n<h3 id=\"3-배열의-초기화\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#3-%EB%B0%B0%EC%97%B4%EC%9D%98-%EC%B4%88%EA%B8%B0%ED%99%94\" aria-label=\"3 배열의 초기화 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>3. 배열의 초기화</h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"java\"><pre class=\"language-java\"><code class=\"language-java\"><span class=\"token comment\">// 1 ~ 10으로 초기화</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">for</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token keyword\">int</span> i <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> i <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span> <span class=\"token number\">10</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token operator\">++</span>i<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  numbers<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>i<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> i <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> <span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"4-배열의-선언과-생성-초기화를-동시에\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#4-%EB%B0%B0%EC%97%B4%EC%9D%98-%EC%84%A0%EC%96%B8%EA%B3%BC-%EC%83%9D%EC%84%B1-%EC%B4%88%EA%B8%B0%ED%99%94%EB%A5%BC-%EB%8F%99%EC%8B%9C%EC%97%90\" aria-label=\"4 배열의 선언과 생성 초기화를 동시에 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>4. 배열의 선언과 생성, 초기화를 동시에</h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"java\"><pre class=\"language-java\"><code class=\"language-java\"><span class=\"token comment\">// 선언과 동시에 생성, 초기화</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">int</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span> arr <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">int</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token number\">3</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> <span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">2</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">3</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">int</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span> arr2 <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> <span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">2</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">3</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"배열의-출력\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EB%B0%B0%EC%97%B4%EC%9D%98-%EC%B6%9C%EB%A0%A5\" aria-label=\"배열의 출력 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>배열의 출력</h2>\n<p>다음 코드처럼 배열의 이름만을 이용해 출력하려고 하면 어떤 결과를 얻을까?</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"java\"><pre class=\"language-java\"><code class=\"language-java\"><span class=\"token keyword\">int</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span> numbers <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> <span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">2</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">3</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">4</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">5</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">6</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">7</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token class-name\">System</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>out<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">println</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>numbers<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">numbers</code>는 배열을 가리키는 참조변수일뿐이다.\n<code class=\"language-text\">타입@메모리주소</code>를 출력한다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">[I@75b84c92</code></pre></div>\n<p>배열의 내용을 출력하려면 다음 방법을 사용한다.</p>\n<h3 id=\"반복문으로-출력하기\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EB%B0%98%EB%B3%B5%EB%AC%B8%EC%9C%BC%EB%A1%9C-%EC%B6%9C%EB%A0%A5%ED%95%98%EA%B8%B0\" aria-label=\"반복문으로 출력하기 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>반복문으로 출력하기</h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"java\"><pre class=\"language-java\"><code class=\"language-java\"><span class=\"token keyword\">int</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span> numbers <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> <span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">2</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">3</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">4</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">5</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">6</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">7</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">for</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token keyword\">int</span> i <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> i <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span> numbers<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>length<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token operator\">++</span>i<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token class-name\">System</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>out<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">print</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>numbers<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>i<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span> <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> <span class=\"token string\">\" \"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<ul>\n<li>반복문으로 배열의 각 인덱스를 순회하며 하나씩 출력하는 방식</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">numbers.length</code>로 배열의 길이를 얻었다.</li>\n<li>We count from zero.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>물론 다음처럼 for-each를 사용하는 것도 가능하다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"java\"><pre class=\"language-java\"><code class=\"language-java\"><span class=\"token keyword\">for</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token keyword\">int</span> n<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> numbers<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token class-name\">System</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>out<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">print</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>n <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> <span class=\"token string\">\" \"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"arraystostring\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#arraystostring\" aria-label=\"arraystostring permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Arrays.toString()</h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"java\"><pre class=\"language-java\"><code class=\"language-java\"><span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> <span class=\"token namespace\">java<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>util<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span></span><span class=\"token class-name\">Arrays</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">public</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">class</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Array</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">public</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">static</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">void</span> <span class=\"token function\">main</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token class-name\">String</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span> args<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">int</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span> numbers <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> <span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=